    "Baykar recorded sales of $1.9 billion in 2023 and its exports rose to $1.8 billion in 2024, thanks to contracts with militaries in Europe, Africa and the Middle East.",
    "Baykar's most famous export, the Bayraktar drone, has been used so successfully by Ukrainian troops that it inspired a popular folk song.",
    "He is the son-in-law of Turkish president Recep Tayyip Erdogan, having married his daughter Sümeyye in 2016."
